<eesti>Tegevuslubade, relvalubade ja relvakandmislubade kehtivus </eesti>
<inglise>Validity of activity licences, weapons permits and permits to carry weapon </inglise>
<eesti>Seni kehtinud &otilde;igusaktide alusel v&auml;ljastatud tegevusload, relvaload ja relvakandmisload kehtivad kuni nende kehtivusaja l&otilde;puni. </eesti>
<inglise>Activity licences, weapons permits and permits to carry a weapon issued on the basis of legislation which was in force prior to the entry into force of this Act are valid until the end of their term. </inglise>
