<inglise>The State Fees Act (RT I 1997, 80, 1344; RT I 2001, 55, 331; 56, 332; 64, 367; 65, 377; 85, 512; 88, 531; 91, 543; 93, 565; 2001, 1, 1; 18, 97; 23, 131; 24, 135; 27, 151 and 153) is amended as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>1) paragrahv 102 muudetakse ja s&otilde;nastatakse j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
<inglise>1) subsection 102 is amended and worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"&sect; 102. </eesti>
<inglise>"&sect; 102. </inglise>
<eesti>Relva soetamisloa, relvaloa, paralleelrelvaloa, relvakandmisloa ja kollektsioneerimisloa v&auml;ljastamine, pikendamine ja vahetamine </eesti>
<inglise>Issue, extension and exchange of weapons acquisition permits, weapons permits, parallel weapons permits, permits to carry a weapon and collection permits </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Relva soetamisloa v&auml;ljastamise eest tasutakse riigil&otilde;ivu 200 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A state fee of 200 kroons shall be paid for the issue of a weapons acquisition permit. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Relvaloa v&auml;ljastamise eest tasutakse riigil&otilde;ivu 200 krooni sile- v&otilde;i vintraudse v&otilde;i kombineeritud jahip&uuml;ssi, gaasip&uuml;stoli v&otilde;i gaasirevolvri registreerimisel ning 2000 krooni muu vintraudse tulirelva registreerimisel. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A state fee of 200 kroons shall be paid for the issue of a weapons permit upon registration of a gun with a smoothbore or rifled barrel or a combination gun, gas pistol or gas revolver, and a state fee of 2000 kroons shall be paid upon registration of any other gun with a rifled barrel. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Paralleelrelvaloa, relvakandmisloa v&otilde;i relvade kollektsioneerimisloa v&auml;ljastamise eest tasutakse riigil&otilde;ivu 200 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) A state fee of 200 kroons shall be paid for the issue of a parallel weapons permit, a permit to carry a weapon or a weapons collection permit. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Relva soetamisloa v&otilde;i relvade kollektsioneerimisloa pikendamise eest tasutakse riigil&otilde;ivu 50 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) A state fee of 50 kroons shall be paid for the extension of a weapons acquisition permit or a weapons collection permit. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Relvaloa, paralleelrelvaloa v&otilde;i relvakandmisloa vahetamise eest tasutakse riigil&otilde;ivu 50 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) A state fee of 50 kroons shall be paid for the exchange of a weapons permit, a parallel weapons permit or a permit to carry a weapon. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Kollektsioneeritava relva andmete kollektsioneerimisloale kandmise eest tasutakse riigil&otilde;ivu 50 krooni." </eesti>
<inglise>(6) A state fee of 50 kroons shall be paid for the entry of information concerning a collectible weapon in a weapons collection permit." </inglise>
